dmca.title: Blogger DMCA Complaint- Caroline Gallagher
dmca.body:
To: Google, Inc.
Attn: Blogger Legal Support, DMCA complaints 

From: Caroline Gallagher 

I am writing today to inform you that photos of my wedding have been illegally used on one 

of your blogs and I would like them removed immediately. I am only one of dozens of 

brides whose photos have been stolen and used without permission. The site in question is: 
http://fakyoucunts.blogspot.com

The photos in question can be found on two separate postings. The first blog post is on 

September 27, 2006 under the title
